{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "乡愁夜空下绽放之花第6话 贤者再临",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "瓦尔法雷依靠惊人的力量得以复活。\\n就在这时，传说中的麒麟族徐福现身。\\n他告诉一行人仙花焰工匠的技术\\n正是打倒瓦尔法雷的关键。\\n王子一行人信其所言，再次进入异界空间。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "唔唔唔唔唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎么会这样……\\n异界裂缝又出现了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我们应该已经打倒了瓦尔法雷啊！\\n究竟是为什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "唔啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "异界裂缝正在闭合……\\n不愧是蓬莱大人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "很遗憾……这只是权宜之计。\\n裂缝马上还会再出现吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "究竟……发生了什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "老夫所担心的事还是发生了。\\n瓦尔法雷……复活了！\\n而且……得到了更强大的力量！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "什……怎、怎么会……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "瓦尔法雷是不断吞噬魔力的\\n贪婪魔兽……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "它真正的强大之处在于能不断吸收周围的\\n魔力，无论被打倒多少次都会复活。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "而且现在它甚至吸收了“黑暗魔力”，\\n由此获得了无穷无尽的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "相当于拥有无限的生命……\\n要怎么才能赢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "怎么能……\\n连蓬莱大人都泄气了可如何是好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "当然不能放任不管！\\n不过……还没有切实可行的手段。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "能请你们……至少先带\\n蓬莱小镇的孩子们去避难吗？\\n就当是老夫这个老头子任性的请求。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "小镇的孩子们……\\n难道是要我们舍弃蓬莱小镇吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "现在最重要的是大家的性命！\\n留得青山在，不愁没柴烧。\\n小镇可以重建！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "小镇……可以重建……\\n可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "蓬莱大人！蓬莱小镇\\n不是普通的小镇……而是我们的故乡！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "你说什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "故乡……永远都不会消失。\\n我不想失去这份美好！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "苏方……可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "蓬莱大人……\\n我曾经忤逆父亲，\\n想在其它小镇推广仙花焰……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "可当时外面的人\\n没有人愿意接受我的仙花焰。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "他们说我是在给他们添麻烦，很碍事。\\n我只好心灰意冷回到故乡。\\n然而等待我的却是父母去世的噩耗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "梦想破灭，又失去了教导我的双亲，\\n而支撑着我走下来的，\\n正是蓬莱小镇……我的故乡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "一如既往的街道……\\n一如既往的爷爷奶奶的笑容……\\n还有……仙花焰。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "本以为我失去了许多，一切都变了。\\n可不曾改变的小镇\\n却告诉了我故乡的美好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "拜托了，蓬莱大人！\\n我需要那个小镇……\\n那个不曾改变的蓬莱小镇！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "蓬、蓬莱大人！我也拜托您了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110268_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "林佑",
            "context": "能不能想想办法，老爷爷！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "唔唔唔……老夫也不想失去小镇。\\n可是，面对现在的瓦尔法雷，\\n要怎么做……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_1014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "说泄气话也没用。\\n这可一点都不像你，蓬莱。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "嗯！？难道是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01",
                "110315_01",
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "众人",
            "context": "徐福大人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "徐福……就是传说中\\n建起了蓬莱小镇的麒麟族吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "蓬莱的孩子们，好久不见了。\\n还有……回应我的呼唤而来的\\n龙之血继承者啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "难怪我觉得这声音似曾相识……\\n在梦里向我传达信息的，\\n果然是你吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "感谢你回应了我的呼唤。\\n要是没有你，\\n应该很难对抗瓦尔法雷吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "听这话……\\n徐福大人，您有对策吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "嗯，为了应对这种状况，\\n我100年前就开始准备了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "我在蓬莱小镇推广仙花焰，\\n也是为了这一刻……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "仙、仙花焰！？春节的娱乐项目\\n对凶恶的魔兽能有什么用……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "仙花焰并不能，\\n但仙花焰工匠可以。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "仙花焰工匠！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "制作仙花焰的时候，\\n要从龙脉泉中准确捕捉流动的魔力，\\n导入仙花焰……也就是导入其它地方。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "只要拥有这种技术，\\n就能将魔力从瓦尔法雷周围排除，\\n从而彻底打倒它。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "100年前我曾想独自完成这件事……\\n但心有余而力不足。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "因此我为了这终将到来的时刻，\\n也为了寻找能助我一臂之力的人，\\n才制作并推广了仙花焰。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "仙花焰工匠身上，\\n还隐藏着这种秘密……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "那、那么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "苏方，有你在的话，\\n这次一定能彻底打倒瓦尔法雷。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "不过为此也需要一个\\n能与之对抗\\n并削弱其力量的强力帮手。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "所以才唤来了\\n尤蒂尔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "嗯。我不能离开异界空间，\\n只能用失礼的方式呼唤你，\\n抱歉啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不……如果没有你的呼唤，\\n如此重要的时刻，\\n我可能什么忙都帮不上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "瓦尔法雷",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "徐福",
            "context": "瓦尔法雷那家伙来了么。\\n龙之血的王子和伙伴们，能拜托你们吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，只要在异界空间里\\n削弱瓦尔法雷就行了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "好！打架我可是不会输的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们一定会拖住瓦尔法雷！\\n各位，我们上！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "好！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_07_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}